Camera
Move the camera up/down by pushing the mouse cursor to top/bottom edge of your screen, where you see the red arrows.\nLikewise, move the camera left/right by pushing the cursor to bottom half of the screen's left/right edge. You may also use assigned hotkeys for this (default: W, A, S, D).\nTo continue, move the camera as indicated by the arrows.

