Camera
Rotate the camera by pushing the cursor to top half of the screen's left/right edge, where you see the red arrows, or by using hotkeys (default: Q, E). If rotating does not work with your mouse, it is disabled in the Game Options menu, which will be looked at shortly. The hotkeys will always work.\nTo continue, move the camera as indicated by the arrows.

