Orders
The orders available for armies can be seen in the Orders Panel, bottom of the screen:\n- Stance: defensive armies will entrench and will not engage enemies in open field battle by default. Offensive armies will remain in higher readiness and will engage any enemy encountered.\n- Army Orders: Allows the army to carry out raiding, guarding or scouting.\n- You already know about construction.\n- Movement orders allow ordering a halt or a forced march. Only units with high readiness (green) can use forced march.\n- Management opens the army management in the military panel. Each order button will show details in its tooltip.

