End of Tutorial
General, the tutorial is over, and you are ready to start learning the game by doing.\nAs was said in the beginning of the tutorial, it only contained the basics of Grand Tactician campaign game play. Remember, at any time you may open the Field Book for instructions. You may also refer to the game's manual, which can be found in the install folder.\nYou may continue to play this scenario without this Tutorial interface, by starting the battle, or to end the scenario via Main Menu.\nIf you choose to lead the battle personally, there will not be a tutorial interface. Battle tutorial can be found in the Historical Battles scenarios.\nGood luck, General!

